#: ../../F/fuel-up.rst:9
msgid ""
"To eat or drink hurriedly in order to get back to hacking. \"Food-p?\" "
"\"Yeah, let's fuel up.\" \"Time for a :ref:`great-wall`\\!\" See also "
":ref:`oriental-food`\\."
msgstr ""
"ハッキングに戻るために、急いで食べたり飲んだりすること。「Food-p?」「ああ、fuel upしよう」「\\ :ref:`great-wall`\\ "
"の時間だ!」。\\ :ref:`oriental-food`\\ も参照。"
